{"word":"G3805 - παθητός - pathētós - path-ay-tos' - Suffer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παθητός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pathētós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">path-ay-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Suffer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பாடுபடவேண்டிய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. passible"},{"paragraph":"2. destined to suffer"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G3804 - πάθημα - páthēma - path'-ay-mah/3804\">G3804</a>; <i>liable</i> (that is, <i>doomed</i>) <i>to</i> experience <i>pain:</i> - suffer.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2552/2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553/2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356/3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663/3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804/3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805/3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806/3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958/3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236/4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310/4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777/4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834/4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835/4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>"}]}